page.title: 13HOME LIFE (CONT)
page.content: CHILD OF 1985(Cont'd) BOOK.I PUT THE TELEVISION ON AND DO MY HOMEWORK.THEN MUM CALLS ME FOR TEA.I SWITCH THE TELEVISION OFF AND GO FOR MY TEA.BY THIS TIME I HAVE FINISHED MY MUSIC WORK.I SIT DOWN AND EAT MY TEA.THEN I GO BACK INTO THE ROOM AND WATCH TELEVISION.THEN AT 7.20 I GET MY MUSIC BAG AND GET INTO THE CAR.MUM OR DAD DRIVES ME THERE.I GET OUT AND GO TO MY MUSIC LESSON.I DO PIANO AND SINGING.AT 8.30 MY MUM COMES TO PICK ME UP.I GO HOME AND HAVE A BATH.THEN I GO DOWN STAIRS FOR A WHILE.I HAVE MY SUPPER.I HAVE SOME CHEESE AND SALAD CREAM.THEN I GO TO BED.I GET INTO BED. KISS MY MUM AND GO TO SLEEP. THE END.
